t_eng: ^Trust me when I say that you'll be paid after this racket.^

column5: I know all there is to know about making the good stuff.^

column5: it's the perfect time to forge yourself one.^

column6: don't tell me that speech about "It's not about the reward.".^

t_eng: ^All these do-gooders can't even appreciate a hero like you.^

^When do I get to be saved?^
